eam! FILM LIVE\" Insert Song Collection|\u300cBanG Dream! FILM LIVE\u300d\u5287\u4e2d\u6b4c\u30b3\u30ec\u30af\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3}} || September 25, 2019 || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animatetimes.com/news/details.php?id=1569384010|title=\u5287\u5834\u7248\u300eBanG Dream! FILM LIVE\u300f\u5287\u4e2d\u6b4c\u30b3\u30ec\u30af\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3\u767a\u58f2\uff01\u3000\u5168\u5287\u4e2d\u6b4c\uff06\u30c9\u30e9\u30de\u30d1\u30fc\u30c8\u53ce\u9332\uff01|work=[[Animate]]|date=September 25, 2019|accessdate=March 21, 2020|language=Japanese|trans-title=Theatrical version \"BanG Dream! FILM LIVE\" insert song collection released! All songs and drama parts included!}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{nihongo|''BanG Dream! Girls Band Party! Cover Collection Vol. 3|\u30d0\u30f3\u30c9\u30ea\uff01 \u30ac\u30fc\u30eb\u30ba\u30d0\u30f3\u30c9\u30d1\u30fc\u30c6\u30a3\uff01 \u30ab\u30d0\u30fc\u30b3\u30ec\u30af\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3 Vol.3}} || December 18, 2019 || Raise A Suilen also featured<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bang-dream.com/discographies/1284|title=Poppin'Party,Afterglow,Pastel\uff0aPalettes ,Roselia,\u30cf\u30ed\u30fc\u3001\u30cf\u30c3\u30d4\u30fc\u30ef\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\uff01,RAISE A SUILEN \u2013 \u30d0\u30f3\u30c9\u30ea\uff01 \u30ac\u30fc\u30eb\u30ba\u30d0\u30f3\u30c9\u30d1\u30fc\u30c6\u30a3\uff01 \u30ab\u30d0\u30fc\u30b3\u30ec\u30af\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3Vol.3|work=BanG Dream!|accessdate=March 21, 2020|language=Japanese|trans-title=Poppin'Party, Afterglow, Pastel\uff0aPalettes, Roselia, Hello, Happy World!, RAISE A SUILEN \u2013 \"BanG Dream! Girls Band Party! Cover Collection Vol.3\"}}</ref>\n|-\n| Poppin'Party<br>Afterglow<br>Pastel\uff0aPalettes<br>Roselia<br>Hello, Happy World!<br>Raise A Suilen<br>Morfonica || {{nihongo|''BanG Dream! Girls Band Party! Cover Collection Vol. 4|\u30d0\u30f3\u30c9\u30ea\uff01 \u30ac\u30fc\u30eb\u30ba\u30d0\u30f3\u30c9\u30d1\u30fc\u30c6\u30a3\uff01 \u30ab\u30d0\u30fc\u30b3\u30ec\u30af\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3 Vol.4}} || May 27, 2020 || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://dengekionline.com/articles/30148/|title=\u300e\u30d0\u30f3\u30c9\u30ea\uff01 \u30ac\u30fc\u30eb\u30ba\u30d0\u30f3\u30c9\u30d1\u30fc\u30c6\u30a3\uff01\u3000\u30ab\u30d0\u30fc\u30b3\u30ec\u30af\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3Vol.4\u300f\u306e\u53ce\u9332\u697d\u66f2\u304c\u767a\u8868|work=Dengeki|date=March 21, 2020|accessdate=March 21, 2020|language=Japanese|trans-title=\"BanG Dream! Girls Band Party!\" Cover Collection Vol.4}}</ref>\n|-\n| Poppin'Party || ''Breakthrough!'' || June 3, 2020 || Poppin'Party's second album<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bang-dream.com/discographies/1691|title=Poppin'Party \u2013 2nd Album\u300cBreakthrough!\u300d|work=BanG Dream!|accessdate=March 21, 2020|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n|-\n| Roselia || ''Wahl'' || July 15, 2020 || Roselia's second album<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bang-dream.com/discographies/1692|title=Roselia \u2013 2nd Album\u300cWahl\u300d|work=BanG Dream!|accessdate=March 21, 2020|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n|-\n| Raise A Suilen || ''Era''{{efn|name=allcaps}} || August 19, 2020 || Raise A Suilen's first album<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bang-dream.com/discographies/1693|title=RAISE A SUILEN \u2013 1st Album\u300cERA\u300d|work=BanG Dream!|accessdate=March 21, 2020|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n====Blu-ray/DVDs====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width: 100%; text-align: center\n|-\n! Artist || Title || Release date || Notes\n|-\n| Poppin'Party || ''Poppin'Party 2015\u20132017 LIVE BEST'' || May 30, 2018 || <ref>{{cite press release|url=https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000001080.000014827.html|title=\u300cBanG Dream!\uff08\u30d0\u30f3\u30c9\u30ea\uff01\uff09\u300d\u3088\u308a5/30(\u6c34)\u767a\u58f2\u3001Poppin\u2019Party\u521d\u306e\u6620\u50cf\u4f5c\u54c1\u300cPoppin\u2019Party 2015-2017 LIVE BEST\u300d\u3092\u30ea\u30ea\u30fc\u30b9\uff01\uff01|agency=PR Times|work=[[Bushiroad]]|date=May 30, 2018|language=Japanese|trans-title=\"BanG Dream!\" will be released on Wednesday, May 30, and Poppin'Party's first video work \"Poppin'Party 2015-2